{"tid":1532684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雙grp奇謀-樹窿&DSE學術支援","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T19:03:55.000Z","uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"309776a6147664d2a1ca0bcce3c0be9875491358","tid":1532684,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問  任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=a26419c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612 <br />\nTG: UuuncleK<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c92ca97322dababe6aa25c4a53e7f397771fd1","tid":1532684,"uid":120412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67d9c2da02e473c3b8bcd0b5f11ccfab42f4193b","tid":1532684,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe8756be9fd152f5a160d9c70a1768df71e5f0f5","tid":1532684,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b70a739f195c7ea54217e16ffb589f483db03ed","tid":1532684,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36406447c37b9726614f9d5ddb899be7ce0eb926","tid":1532684,"uid":120412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0d636959a2dff06465bac045f82a33ed35fabce","tid":1532684,"uid":120412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:55:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2a6e3757a2950ad6e1ea76a036bfc11de85f75d7","tid":1532684,"uid":120412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68b7584bf7f6166c7878b5a5f36ec119a8ea4f9d","tid":1532684,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab5bde9214e4880c7153d1438f6876525c2bd300","tid":1532684,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2